show.description: After years of being the perfect girlfriend and dutiful daughter, Kristine Wilson's life of compromise shatters when she discovers her fiancé's betrayal. Already scarred by her family's abuse, this final deception ignites something dangerous within her. Fed up with being everyone's doormat, Kristine hatches a scandalous plan for vengeance that will shake the foundations of her world. In a calculated power move, she seduces Henry Lockwood—her cheating fiancé's powerful uncle and heir to the family fortune. What begins as sweet revenge evolves into a dangerous game of passion and power where the stakes couldn't be higher. In this provocative tale of betrayal and redemption, Kristine must decide if revenge is worth the price of becoming someone she never thought she'd be.
